# Accordion

**Figma:** [Accordion](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=128-10528&p=f&m=dev)

Header variants, content structure, layout variants, and states below are derived from Figma node 128:10528.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Header/content bg | `--bg-base-tertiary` or `--bg-base-secondary` |
| Border | `--border-base-default` |
| Body text | `--text-base-secondary` |
| Chevron | `--text-brand-default` |
| Chevron emphasis | `--bg-brand-tertiary` circle |
| Status error | `--bg-danger-default` |
| Status success | `--bg-success-default` |
| Status warning | `--bg-warning-default` |

---

## Structure

### Header
- **Layout:** Checkbox (left); Title (bold); optional Status text + status dot; optional Label; Chevron (right).
- **Variants:** Full (checkbox, title, status, label, chevron); Simplified (checkbox, title, chevron only).

### Content
- Revealed below header when expanded.
- Body: `--text-base-secondary`.
- Padding: Space/200–400.

---

## States

| State | Chevron | Content |
|-------|---------|---------|
| Collapsed | Down | Hidden |
| Expanded | Up | Visible |

---

## Layout variants

| Variant | Items | Separator |
|---------|-------|-----------|
| Stacked | Touch | `border-bottom` `--border-base-default` 1px |
| Spaced | Space/200–300 between | Subtle shadow or border |

---

## Styling

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Radius | Radius/100 (4px) or Radius/200 (8px) |
| Chevron emphasis | Within `--bg-brand-tertiary` circle |

### Status dot
| Type | Token |
|------|-------|
| Error/urgent | `--bg-danger-default` |
| Success | `--bg-success-default` |
| Attention | `--bg-warning-default` |

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- A11y: `aria-expanded`, `aria-controls`; keyboard (Enter/Space to toggle); focus on header.
- Smooth height animation: `transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out`.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 128:10528.
